Had the idea on Monday, found the exact part on a bench in Shenzhen by lunch, and it was on my doorstep before the week was out. A factory, a freight forwarder, a customs desk, and a driver I'll never meet each touched that little box so I could build the idea while it was still fresh. An ocean crossed, so a good idea didn't have to wait.
